      },
      "source": [
        "#Step 1-3 string 轉成 dictionary \n",
        "* 1. 抓回來是r 是物件  //r=requests.get(url)\n",
        "* 2. 先抓res=r.text, //res即是 string (res=r.text)\n",
        "* 3. json.loads(res) 轉成 dictionary\n",
        "* 4. python 即可讀到\n",
        "\n",
        "HW4-1 第一個要求：印出 uri\n",
        "\n",
        "\n"
      ]
    },
